  "texts": [
    "Standardized evaluation metrics are needed to determine the level of syntheticism of SDs [34].",
    "The images should be \"synthetic\" enough to avoid any resemblance to real images, and \"realistic\" enough to be applicable to real-world scenarios.",
    "Before SDs can be employed for training AI, its realism needs to be determined by a subject expert [1,35].",
